            <item>II. Letter Copybooks, 1937-1941</item>
            <item>III. Compiled Volumes, 1925-1980</item>
            <item>IV. Biographical Documentation, 1925-1926, n.d.</item>
            <item>V. Addendum: 2010, 1925-1946, n.d.</item>
         </list>
      </arrangement>
